S' during the reign of ibrahim qutb shah, the fourth king of golconda became a market for the whole world. merchants from turkey, arabia, and persia were so well treated that they used to visit golconda frequently. during mohamed qutb shah\xe2\x80\x99s time, the dutch established themselves at machilipatnam in 1615 and the english in 1622.'
